d 'XTTESTPANEL': module to perform post-estimation diagnostic test suite for linear panel-data models
d
d	 xttestpanel is a unified library of modern post-estimation
d diagnostic tests for linear panel-data regressions. Each
d subcommand	estimates the requested model internally (fixed
d effects, random effects, two-way, or pooled), extracts the
d residuals, computes	 the relevant battery of tests, prints a
d clean formatted table, and -- with the graph option -- produces a
d publication-quality	 diagnostic plot.  The all subcommand runs
d everything and adds a colour-coded decision summary and an
d optional combined    dashboard. 
d
d KW:  panel data
d KW: fixed effects
d KW: random effects
d KW: graphics
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260612
d
d Author:   Merwan Roudane, NA
d Support: email  merwanroudane920@@gmail.com
d
f xttestpanel_example.do
f xttestpanel_postestimation_example.do
f xttestpanel.ado
f xttestpanel_csd.sthlp
f xttestpanel_func.sthlp
f xttestpanel_hausman.sthlp
f xttestpanel_het.sthlp
f xttestpanel_postestimation.sthlp
f xttestpanel_serial.sthlp
f xttestpanel_vif.sthlp
f xttestpanel.sthlp
